Head . Transverse, black, slightly wider than pronotum. Frons weakly convex. Palpi yellow. Punctuation dense and fine. Pubescence double, dense, wholly, white, homogeneous, largely covering the tegument. Eyes nearly reaching the posterior edge of the head in side view, or separated from it by a strip of tegument narrower than the width of a row of ommatidia (
Figure 2t
).
